   WELCOME!

      A part of the United States District Court, the United States Probation
      Office for the Southern District of Illinois assists the Court in both
      probation and pretrial functions through investigating and supervising
      individuals charged with or convicted of Federal crimes. The Probation
      Office provides coverage for 38 counties in Southern Illinois. In
      addition to the headquarters office in East St. Louis, a divisional
      office is located in Benton.
